  "remarks": "Has actively undermined democracy in Belarus. Former Сhairman of the Regional Election Committee of the Gomel region, former Member of the Lower Chamber of the Parliament. As Chairman of a Regional Electoral Commission, he was directly responsible for the violations of international electoral standards, in particular in the Presidential elections in 2006 in the Gomel region.",
